---
title: Podcast Player
---

%header.hero
  %h1 Aroid
  %p.tagline Listen to what matters to you.
  %p.hero-desc
    Your time is valuable. Aroid puts you in control of every minute —
    so you can focus on the content you actually came for. All running
    locally on the powerful device already in your pocket.
  %a.cta{href: '#'} Download on TestFlight

%section.features
  %h2 What Aroid does
  .feature-grid
    .feature
      %h3 Understands every episode
      %p
        Aroid analyzes each episode to identify who is speaking and what
        kind of content is in each segment — interview, commentary, sponsor
        read, whatever it might be. That understanding drives everything else.
    .feature
      %h3 Navigate any episode
      %p
        Speaker detection and content analysis combine to auto-generate
        chapters for every episode. See who's talking and what's being
        discussed, then jump straight there — no scrubbing required.
    .feature
      %h3 Skips what you don't want
      %p
        Once Aroid knows what's in an episode, it can move past the parts
        you didn't come for. Automatically, before you even press play.

%section.ondevice
  %h2 All of this runs on your device
  %p
    Most apps that do any kind of audio analysis send your content to a
    server to do the heavy lifting. Aroid doesn't. Transcription, speaker
    detection, content classification — everything is computed locally,
    using the powerful hardware already in your pocket or on your desk.
  %p
    Your audio never leaves your device. No accounts, no cloud processing,
    no one else's servers involved.

%section.pitch
  %p
    Your time is finite, listen to what matters to you.

%footer
  %p &copy; #{Time.now.year}
